<div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">   .start Start<br /><br />   .org $0000<br /><br />Variable1: .rs 2<br />Variable2: .rs 1<br />Variable3: .rs 2<br />   <br />   .org $8000<br />   <br />Start:<br />   ;execution will start here!<br />   lda #$50<br />   sta Variable2</div><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=95">tokumaru</a> — Wed Jun 24, 2009 5:44 pm</p><hr />
